{"tid":1146304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：會考慮與美方商討將何志平移交本港服刑","createTime":"2019-05-09T07:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T15:23:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5d106833fb73ba98c3b13ceb71ba819d76aa778b","tid":1146304,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"新民黨議員葉劉淑儀在立法會行政長官答問會表示，前民政事務局局長何志平在美國因行賄被定罪，判囚3年。她問林鄭月娥，香港與美國有移交判刑人士的協議，若何志平放棄上訴，會否考慮與美方商討將何志平移交返香港服刑，也可以讓他在醫院休息，減少辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，會讓保安局局長研究一下兩地的有關安排，以及法律基礎由哪一方提出，強調會用一個以人為本的角度去考慮。葉劉淑儀補充說，以她理解，只要三方同意便可以移交，林鄭月娥表示會考慮。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1456737-20190509.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1456737-20190509.htm&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=6139cb82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1456737-20190509.htm&h=5bca74d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1456737-20190509.htm</a>"},{"pid":"da67410f9a4ad9362b6fededb458959584f8c8f7","tid":1146304,"uid":1989,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"返香港命就冇硬<br />\n為国服務應該都有條全屍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd3a10e492f4612457cba43360a7b66903adf2c","tid":1146304,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"455b4eefbe3f29fcba325e6ec62bdafb0db857f8","tid":1146304,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"細路祥等緊你"},{"pid":"a10cf7aa36b2ba04b95e37276380ebc49ba5c223","tid":1146304,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"何志平rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959be5b42a8b58b99b8da0731555d62519a56b